You mentioned Fincher likes to do a lot of takes.

16:24.280 --> 16:27.720
That's the, the famous thing about David Fincher.

16:28.280 --> 16:29.960
So what are the pros and cons of that?

16:30.480 --> 16:34.400
I think I read that he does some crazy amount.

