didn't do. So I also should say that the thing I hope to do here is to

01:13:39.720 --> 01:13:47.080
give respect to due process, innocent until proven guilty that the mass hysteria machine of

01:13:47.880 --> 01:13:54.600
the internet and clickbait journalism doesn't do. So here's what I understand.

01:13:55.480 --> 01:13:59.640
